一句话总结：
COT+Plan-Execute是FunctionCall的
"操作系
没有COT,模型不知道怎么拆任务；
1、COT让模型"讲清楚任务'
2、Plan让模型"按顺序做任务"
3、Execute让模型"逐步执行工具"
没有Plan-Execute,
任务拆对了也跑不稳。
4、Observe让模型"看到API结果"
5、Reflection让模型"自己修正错误"
这套闭环，就是现实世界Agent系统的"操作系统"
在吴师兄大模型训练营的Agent项目里，这套体系是强制要求与在系统prompt、执行链路
里的，因为：这套方法，不是为了炫酷，而是为了能稳定跑。]]></one:OCRText><one:OCRToken startPos="0" region="0" line="0" x="26.49999809265137" y="13.00000095367432" width="19.49999809265137" height="19.5"/><one:OCRToken startPos="1" region="0" line="0" x="47.49999618530273" y="27.0" width="5.999999523162841" height="5.500000476837158"/><one:OCRToken startPos="2" region="0" line="0" x="67.49999237060547" y="13.00000095367432" width="19.99999809265137" height="19.5"/><one:OCRToken startPos="3" region="0" line="0" x="88.5" y="13.00000095367432" width="19.99999809265137" height="20.0"/><one:OCRToken startPos="4" region="0" line="0" x="111.9999923706055" y="18.5" width="3.999999761581421" height="12.0"/><one:OCRToken startPos="6" region="0" line="1" x="13.99999904632568" y="106.0" width="14.49999904632568" height="1.5"/><one:OCRToken startPos="7" region="0" line="1" x="28.99999809265137" y="99.99999237060547" width="13.49999904632568" height="14.5"/><one:OCRToken startPos="8" region="0" line="1" x="44.0" y="100.5" width="14.49999904632568" height="14.0"/><one:OCRToken startPos="9" region="0" line="1" x="58.99999237060547" y="99.99999237060547" width="14.49999904632568" height="14.0"/><one:OCRToken startPos="10" region="0" line="1" x="73.99999237060547" y="99.99999237060547" width="14.99999809265137" height="14.5"/><one:OCRToken startPos="11" region="0" line="1" x="91.49999237060547" y="104.0000076293945" width="2.499999761581421" height="9.0"/><one:OCRToken startPos="13" region="1" line="2" x="130.4999847412109" y="14.0" width="39.5" height="16.5"/><one:OCRToken startPos="16" region="1" line="2" x="178.9999847412109" y="18.5" width="10.5" height="10.50000095367432"/><one:OCRToken startPos="17" region="1" line="2" x="199.9999694824219" y="13.5" width="132.4999847412109" height="17.0"/><one:OCRToken startPos="29" region="1" line="2" x="339.4999694824219" y="13.5" width="19.99999809265137" height="19.5"/><one:OCRToken startPos="30" region="1" line="2" x="367.9999694824219" y="13.5" width="88.0" height="